replies.body:
Fuck yes riot please do this i missed out on project border for zed by a single day, i was in perth ;-;
but yeah other than my personal gain this would be good fun if you didnt have time for a full game you can just make some borders. i also think its smart to pay ip to get a border on a certain champ, maybe half the amount the champ costs. this is probs better than one border for everything because it might get in the way of some splashes. also you can make it fit the theme. please make it more ip based though i dont want it to be pay to look cool, more of you spend your time making it to look cool, after all it would take ages. also with this another thing, make it so when you are creating them you can export the file and import it (gotta be a special file type though just for this) and yeah when creating it also allow symmetrical mode you you only have to do one side and the other mirrors it (optional)
rito this took a long time to write, and i beg that you implement this as soon as you can it would be awesome :3
